lm.height <- lm(HT18 ~ HT2, data=BGSall)
par(mfrow=c(1,3))

#residuals vs. fitted-values plo
plot(lm.height, which=1:2)


# residuals vs. order
plot(lm.height$residuals,
     main="Residuals Vs. Order")
